<ol>
  <li>
    <p>He became <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="disoriented"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(晕头转向)</code></b> and suffered from <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="sudden fainting spells (spell：突然的发作)"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(突然昏厥)</code></b>.</p>
